|1965
!
|Pont Rhydgaled
|The first bridge over the Wye, {{convert|3.2|km|mi}} below it's source. A steel beam structure with a wooden deck, {{convert|10|m|ft}} long with two cylindrical columns mid-span.
|<ref name=crow>{{cite book |first=Alan |last=Crow |title=Bridges on the River Wye |publisher=Lapridge Publications |location=Hereford |isbn=0-9518589-9-8 |date=1995}}</ref>
